Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:11.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.24,0:00:13.53,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么是笹目呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.20,0:00:17.33,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,赤司他只是搞错了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.41,0:00:19.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是的 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.96,0:00:26.13,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有做错任何事的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.46,0:00:29.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以一定没问题的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.21,0:00:32.09,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,赤司
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.56,0:00:54.03,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}にじんでる歩道橋のらくがき
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.20,0:01:05.25,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}置いてかれた自転車　誰かの帰りを待ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.25,0:01:10.42,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}認めて　ただ存在を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.88,0:01:13.05,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}僕こそがオリジナル
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.55,0:01:15.55,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}あるいはそのレプリカ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.01,0:01:20.01,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}僕らの証明はどこにある
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.26,0:01:24.85,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}人類の欠点は　見えもしないくせに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.35,0:01:30.11,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}愛とか絆とか信じられること
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.48,0:01:35.03,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}僕の罪はうたがったこと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.32,0:01:38.20,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}差し伸べられた君の右手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.57,0:01:41.16,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}初めて見たヒカリ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.91,0:01:50.21,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}僕らは———
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.56,0:00:54.03,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,岁月流转　天桥涂鸦终归消散
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.20,0:01:05.25,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,静置难安　单车默待谁人与共还
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.25,0:01:10.42,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,坦然直面　存在世间　身外孑然一片
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.88,0:01:13.05,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,却难断　吾乃本源
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.55,0:01:15.55,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,抑或水月云烟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.01,0:01:20.01,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,孰真孰幻　吾等安辩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.26,0:01:24.85,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,人心缺点难免　未曾得见
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.35,0:01:30.11,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,爱与羁绊　却坚信依然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.48,0:01:35.03,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,心疑难掩　吾罪何堪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.32,0:01:38.20,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,与君右手紧牵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.57,0:01:41.16,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,唯慨叹　光明初现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.91,0:01:50.21,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,吾等只盼……
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.98,0:02:10.48,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(145,700)\fad(1029,1029)}第二十话\N爱之重音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.73,0:02:16.11,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我去过读岛了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.49,0:02:18.82,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,大海真的很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.11,0:02:22.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我还记得你在看海时说的那些话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.41,0:02:25.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,怀念的事高兴的事什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.21,0:02:29.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,以后有机会讲给我听吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.01,0:02:46.39,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,当年读岛的惨剧想必各位也有所耳闻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.56,0:02:48.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.19,0:02:51.06,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你们就打算装傻到底吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.69,0:02:52.27,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,比起翻这种陈年老账
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:57.57,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,MA-Vess要是修理完成了的话\N就赶快派往无明领域继续调查
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.90,0:02:58.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,恕难从命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.20,0:03:03.03,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,眼下骸已复活 贸然行动只会重蹈覆辙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.45,0:03:05.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.87,0:03:06.54,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,恕我失礼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.95,0:03:10.42,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你们根本不了解情况又谈何决策
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.04,0:03:15.29,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,故请将今后的行动全权委托于我须崎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:16.13,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,须崎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.38,0:03:17.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,简直胡闹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.51,0:03:22.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你说我不行 你行你上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.89,0:03:24.80,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,眼下妹尾与夏入都已牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:28.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,列位可否有将全责一己承担的觉悟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.98,0:03:33.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,列位全无异议了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:37.23,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那帮家伙根本就不了解现状
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:39.99,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,也不在乎当初所犯下的罪业
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.86,0:03:45.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,今后石像鬼小队将把战胜骸作为首要任务
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.66,0:03:49.95,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,但这并不意味着要替IX护短
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.96,0:03:53.92,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,打倒骸真的能解决眼下这些问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.13,0:03:56.38,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,笠音 有劳了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.46,0:03:57.92,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.09,0:04:01.42,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,基本可以确定创造出无明领域的源头
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.92,0:04:04.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,就是骸体内的无明石
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.60,0:04:07.60,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能对它进行彻底研究的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:10.68,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,或许这一切就能有个解答了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.77,0:04:13.64,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说不打倒骸的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.90,0:04:15.86,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,就一切都无从谈起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:19.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,以前夏入也说要是能深入研究骸的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.90,0:04:22.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定能让尸钢化的人复原的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:23.57,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,是说过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.95,0:04:28.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定艾米露和笹目也…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.34,0:04:42.51,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,研究员也比以前少了很多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:47.47,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一定也都有更加期待的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.43,0:04:53.10,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,可是鸫她…还有读岛的人们…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.19,0:04:54.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,真亚梦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.27,0:04:58.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我很担心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.48,0:05:03.15,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,以我绵薄之力到底能不能拯救大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.40,0:05:08.28,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定可以 也说不定就不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.24,0:05:11.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,自己到底能做到什么程度谁又说得清楚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.83,0:05:13.33,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.08,0:05:16.79,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,说到底无非就是自我满足嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.38,0:05:20.84,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,但我现在觉得这也无可厚非
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.34,0:05:24.55,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,至少为自己问心无愧努力过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.18,0:05:29.35,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我真心希望笹目和艾米露能复原
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:31.51,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,也在为此而努力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.52,0:05:34.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就好了 不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:40.27,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,暂时就只能吃这些了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.61,0:05:46.03,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 赤司？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.90,0:05:47.15,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,笠音姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.49,0:05:48.03,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,赤司
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.41,0:05:49.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,方便借一步说话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.20,0:05:53.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 正巧我也有话想跟你说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.95,0:05:54.83,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,0:05:58.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,就是关于最近你和银的共信…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.33,0:06:01.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,算了去找来夏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.01,0:06:06.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.38,0:06:08.84,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,从早上起脸色就不太好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:11.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.68,0:06:14.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 那时发生了什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:16.35,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:21.27,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那时你和银的共信率高得让人无法理解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.52,0:06:25.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉和平时有什么不同吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.78,0:06:28.49,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…好像确实有点不可思议的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.90,0:06:31.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,好像银比自己的身体还要轻盈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.95,0:06:34.33,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,界联系统呢 有什么异样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:37.29,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,没 和平时差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.04,0:06:41.00,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会有那么高的共信率呢 你有头绪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.67,0:06:46.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得可能是我和哥哥的心意合而为一的关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.47,0:06:48.97,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,心意合而为一…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.43,0:06:53.60,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 不愿失去所爱之人的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.47,0:06:58.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,为此即便不知道自己能做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:01.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,也绝不能袖手旁观的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.15,0:07:06.32,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这么一说感觉挺傻的不过那时就是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.90,0:07:08.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得哥哥他也是一样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:12.45,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,但不知是否受其影响
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.66,0:07:17.29,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,有种不知是平静还是疏远的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.79,0:07:20.29,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,笠音姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.96,0:07:22.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对不起 我没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:36.14,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会和哥哥一起打倒骸的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.47,0:07:40.98,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,到时无明石就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.77,0:07:44.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,只要拿到东西 笹目和艾米露就能复原了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.48,0:07:46.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥一定也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.44,0:07:51.28,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是想告诉你我的决心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:01.75,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会有办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.21,0:08:08.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以拜托你不要离我而去啊 青司
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.46,0:08:11.92,Text,,0,0,0,,{\an3\pos(934,421)\c&H030304&\3c&HFFFFFF&\3a&H3C&}多谢大家一贯关照\N今天小店管喝管够\N——店主
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.01,0:08:13.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.31,0:08:25.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,夏入这一死 技术上大家就都要靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.98,0:08:27.06,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:29.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道自己能做到什么程度
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:32.15,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,总之先尽力而为吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:35.16,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这话是跟青司学来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.82,0:08:36.91,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,赤司他跟我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.07,0:08:37.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.33,0:08:42.54,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,在银上和青司的心意合而为一了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.04,0:08:47.84,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 到现在青司也还是老样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.05,0:08:50.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,然后你就想说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:55.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么宁可和男人互相理解都要拒绝我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:08:56.76,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:09:01.35,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有 又不是不知道他溺爱弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.22,0:09:05.69,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得不愿让你担心这才是他的男子汉气概啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.65,0:09:12.61,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,在无明领域里失去的东西已经太多太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:16.45,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,到底该做什么怎么做谁也说不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.49,0:09:19.58,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,至于说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.16,0:09:23.33,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,就专心努力让青司复原吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:25.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,就别去管什么别的了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.21,0:09:32.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,笠音？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.13,0:09:33.76,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,须酱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.92,0:09:35.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.47,0:09:37.09,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,青司他…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.47,0:09:40.76,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,青司的界联系统
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.72,0:09:43.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有点不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:45.27,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不对劲？怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.85,0:09:50.23,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,很多零星的地方都和平常不太一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:52.98,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在都不敢去检查他的数据
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.03,0:10:00.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 肯定是我多心了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.58,0:10:02.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定是太累了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.99,0:10:04.83,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,须酱 咱们喝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.29,0:10:11.38,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这话我也不是第一次说了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:16.47,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不要为青司去无明领域这事再责怪自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.09,0:10:19.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那都是青司他自己的决定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.39,0:10:21.18,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.14,0:10:27.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说向共信模块复制的人格是不是不完整
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.06,0:10:28.98,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.60,0:10:30.23,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.86,0:10:34.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,将其与鹭沼的共信测试再多进行几次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.61,0:10:35.82,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,取得更加准确的数据再…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.11,0:10:38.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,拘泥于这种问题那要几百辈子才能有点进展啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.20,0:10:42.45,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…要是有个万一的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.53,0:10:44.83,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,青司都说了他要去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.91,0:10:46.83,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,但进入无明领域万一…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.87,0:10:50.71,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不去进行验证的话那就永远都只是假说了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.38,0:10:55.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,他可是要为心爱的你的研究出一份力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.13,0:11:02.34,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是无法肆意践踏他的这分心意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.52,0:11:07.68,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,要我背你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.52,0:11:09.10,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不用啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.86,0:11:15.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 我是和夏入那样说过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.57,0:11:17.61,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你不后悔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.24,0:11:21.99,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,要去那种地方 老实说还是挺害怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.70,0:11:24.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果是我力所能及的话我也不想逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.95,0:11:29.33,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,笠音为新型Vess开发所做的努力我也都有看在眼里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.29,0:11:33.58,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要用我认为最能回应你努力的方式去努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.34,0:11:37.34,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会成功完成任务回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.55,0:11:41.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,也要让赤司看看哥哥帅气的样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.14,0:11:47.10,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也知道你心里的苦 可这担子也只有你能扛了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.89,0:11:48.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.65,0:11:59.57,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,夏入他私自保管的数据里一定会有线索才对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.74,0:12:07.53,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,早知道从医务室拿点止痛药好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.58,0:12:09.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,医院…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.87,0:12:13.71,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说是那家医院
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.17,0:12:16.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,显示出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.75,0:12:21.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那里应该在银启动之后就废弃了才对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.59,0:12:26.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,但也已经没有别的可能性了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.10,0:12:28.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,只能在这里赌一把了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.43,0:12:33.35,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,废弃医院？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.10,0:12:37.11,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,在作为银的开发设施使用之前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.36,0:12:40.11,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,是接收因无明领域尸钢化的患者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:44.03,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,供夏入秘密进行界联系统研究的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.82,0:12:46.49,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说完全废弃之后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,0:12:49.99,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,夏入仍将其作为实验室在使用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.94,0:13:22.28,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,基本都是公开的数据啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.86,0:13:24.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.11,0:13:25.95,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,服务器？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.32,0:13:29.95,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,是这台啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.41,0:13:33.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,看来这里的数据就是希望所在了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.50,0:13:37.92,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,青司 再等等哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.17,0:13:47.09,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是骸的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.60,0:13:59.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到那医院竟有如此内情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.86,0:14:00.69,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.86,0:14:03.44,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,银应该没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.69,0:14:09.03,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 笠音姐她也在努力着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.91,0:14:14.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,心怀着对你们三个成为界联系统这份罪业的自责…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.75,0:14:18.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,即便知道她心中的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.17,0:14:23.25,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,却仍愿默默地守护着她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.34,0:14:26.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是哥哥你的罪业吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.72,0:14:30.51,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,守护心爱之人的这份心意也算是罪业的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.55,0:14:35.43,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,又要怎样才能得到救赎呢 哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:40.23,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,是笠音吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.27,0:14:42.82,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,须酱快来救我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.20,0:14:49.49,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,笠音 出什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.07,0:14:51.57,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,须酱 有戒缚…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.70,0:14:56.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,被吞掉了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.25,0:14:59.54,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 这样下去的话服务器也有危险
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.21,0:15:06.76,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你倒是来追我呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.22,0:15:12.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,来呀 这边 快来呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.35,0:15:14.39,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,戒缚这…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.56,0:15:16.14,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,是在那医院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.39,0:15:17.06,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.02,0:15:21.90,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,从这里到废弃医院还要多久
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.94,0:15:22.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,十三分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.86,0:15:29.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,银这共信率…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.07,0:15:32.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这感觉之前也有过一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.87,0:15:34.32,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,赤司 你还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.95,0:15:35.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,让一让
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.58,0:15:37.33,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,先走一步
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.00,0:15:42.62,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,赤司 不要胡来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.88,0:15:45.54,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,银的共信率突破理论上限
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:50.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.43,0:15:53.68,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,又是之前那样的紧密联结…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.18,0:15:57.43,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,总之眼下就是要尽力而为 你说是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.64,0:15:59.98,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这都是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.86,0:16:12.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙变得越来越大了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.74,0:16:13.28,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,抓紧时间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.41,0:16:58.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事 怎么自己就动起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.41,0:17:01.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,笠音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.25,0:17:05.37,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,伤囗不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.25,0:17:08.92,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,死神竟开口说话了…不…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.04,0:17:10.13,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,是青司吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.71,0:17:16.34,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,现在这台机体就像是自己的身体一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.22,0:17:21.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,举手投足 眼中所见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.73,0:17:26.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,笠音你的面容也清晰可辨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.35,0:17:27.31,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,青司
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.74,0:17:42.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我感觉到那东西就是想要活人的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.75,0:17:45.12,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.00,0:17:51.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那声音不是赤司的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.59,0:17:52.75,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,到底发生什么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.76,0:17:56.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,机师和界联系统间发生了啸鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.97,0:17:58.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,现在保护遮断器已经启动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.80,0:18:00.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,已将发往界联系统的外部信号全部屏蔽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.78,0:18:14.28,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,青司
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.12,0:18:23.79,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也能行 我也能行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.62,0:18:27.12,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,青司 住手吧 不要再战斗了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.66,0:18:30.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,共信率已经超过上限了 这样不行的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.29,0:18:31.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:34.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道会给你造成多大的负担啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.21,0:18:36.09,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这样太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.01,0:18:39.55,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不要再战斗了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.18,0:18:42.18,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了 青司
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.64,0:18:46.10,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你就听我劝一次好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.39,0:18:50.15,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,青司
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.23,0:18:54.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的会死的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.66,0:19:03.45,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.62,0:19:07.12,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,银的界联系统停机了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.50,0:19:08.16,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.67,0:19:11.12,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,青司
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.83,0:19:13.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.67,0:19:16.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.17,0:19:18.55,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你快回答我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.51,0:19:25.81,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.56,0:19:28.10,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.48,0:19:30.69,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,动啊 给我动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.90,0:19:33.69,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,界联系统死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.77,0:19:34.69,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.48,0:19:38.28,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,真亚梦 银已经无法战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.69,0:19:40.03,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那戒缚就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.32,0:19:41.36,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.66,0:19:50.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,真亚梦 真亚梦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.00,0:19:54.54,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,青司
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.29,0:19:57.30,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,青司 快说话呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.55,0:20:01.72,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,青司
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.76,0:20:08.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,青司 不要走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.56,0:20:13.27,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我要你永远活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.15,0:20:16.15,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,永远留在我身边啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.28,0:20:22.95,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我还想再和你十指相抵啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.88,0:20:40.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.49,0:21:04.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,笠…音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.78,0:21:09.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,青司
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.46,0:21:18.08,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想再轻抚你的面颊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.13,0:21:21.42,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不过好像时间要到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.84,0:21:23.51,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.59,0:21:32.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,笠音 不要再愁眉苦脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.27,0:21:34.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,像以前一样开怀欢笑吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.87,0:21:52.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,青司
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.40,0:22:25.03,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.03,0:22:29.91,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.41,0:22:32.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,青司
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.22,0:22:58.06,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You lose your mind, you crash
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.31,0:22:59.94,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}A nervous breakdown
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.35,0:23:02.90,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You feel an urge inside, you crush
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.11,0:23:04.57,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}There's no escape now
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.19,0:23:07.74,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You try to change your life, you jump
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.82,0:23:09.49,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Another letdown
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.90,0:23:12.66,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}But then you hear a voice inside
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.66,0:23:14.28,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You gotta open up your vision
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.37,0:23:15.91,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}See the life bestowed on you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.99,0:23:18.12,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Blinded by reality
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.41,0:23:20.67,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Broken ideology
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.75,0:23:23.17,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Heart in captivity
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.25,0:23:24.04,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hold on
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.13,0:23:25.34,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Exceeding the borders within
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.59,0:23:27.92,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Seize your capability
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.96,0:23:30.38,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Endless possibility
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.38,0:23:32.76,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Find your individuality
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.80,0:23:34.47,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Take pride, let the chase begin
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.60,0:23:37.93,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Don't tell me what direction you think I should take
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.47,0:23:39.39,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}『I know I'm gonna find the way』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.31,0:23:42.48,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Don't tell me that this sable is for my own sake
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.48,0:23:44.27,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}『Hear what I've got to say』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.19,0:23:47.23,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Don't tell me to believe the decisions you make
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.03,0:23:49.11,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}『I'm facing a new day』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.94,0:23:51.65,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}So open up your blinded eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.78,0:23:54.12,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Stop living a lie and start living your life
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.37,0:23:56.24,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}My way or no way
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.66,0:23:58.95,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Today you're falling away
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.29,0:24:00.83,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}My way or no way
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.46,0:24:03.88,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Today I'm breaking away
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.22,0:22:58.06,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,失汝心志　躯形难继
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.31,0:22:59.94,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,慌乱分崩离析
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.35,0:23:02.90,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,心潮涌动　冲荡破碎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.11,0:23:04.57,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,已是无路可退
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.19,0:23:07.74,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,逆天改命　奋力跃腾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.82,0:23:09.49,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,再落心灰意冷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.90,0:23:12.66,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,却闻心中轻语
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.66,0:23:14.28,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,放眼茫然四顾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.37,0:23:15.91,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,但见尘世夺予
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.99,0:23:18.12,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,现实毁盲双目
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.41,0:23:20.67,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,仅余碎裂思悟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.75,0:23:23.17,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,心亦牢牢禁锢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.25,0:23:24.04,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,勿言轻弃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.13,0:23:25.34,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,跨越心中束缚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.59,0:23:27.92,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,紧握汝力天成
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.96,0:23:30.38,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,迸发无尽可能
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.38,0:23:32.76,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,寻汝真我个性
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.80,0:23:34.47,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,昂首迈步前行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.60,0:23:37.93,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,莫要擅自定吾前路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.47,0:23:39.39,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,『吾定将自寻通途』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.31,0:23:42.48,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,莫言黑暗皆为吾敌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.48,0:23:44.27,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,『但得静闻吾倾诉』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.19,0:23:47.23,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,莫诳吾从尔等好恶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.03,0:23:49.11,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,『吾自面崭新朝暮』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.94,0:23:51.65,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,故舍犹豫再开盲眼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.78,0:23:54.12,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,挣脱谎言自立世间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.37,0:23:56.24,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,足下再无别途
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.66,0:23:58.95,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,此时汝却飘然离去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.29,0:24:00.83,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,足下再无别途
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.46,0:24:03.88,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,今日吾将突破禁锢
